      <item>
        <title>User Guide</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/tyburg/disconnected-content-explorer-examples/raw/master/DICEUserGuide.zip&quot;&gt;Download DICEUserGuide.zip&lt;/a&gt; After clicking the link chose “Open in DICE.”&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/userguide.png&quot; alt=&quot;User Guide Screenshot&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The user guide example is a bit of dogfooding, using example content to show this app can be used.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you can display it in a browser using HTML5, CSS, and Javascript, odds are you can take that content offline with DICE, as long as you keep your data local and relatively linked. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When creating your own content for DICE, you can add a metadata.json file to let the app know how to display your content in the list, tile, and map views. If you do not set a title, the filename minus the extension will be used.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;An example metadata.json&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-json&quot; data-lang=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;title&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;DICE User Guide&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;description&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;A brief overview of this app&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;thumbnail&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;img/thumbnail.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;tile_thumbnail&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;img/tilethumb.png&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;reportID&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;userguide1.0&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;lat&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;0.0&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;lon&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;0.0&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Feel free to pull this report out of DICE and poke around in the code.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Resources used to create the user guide: &lt;a href=&quot;http://getbootstrap.com/&quot;&gt;Bootstrap&lt;/a&gt; for layout, &lt;a href=&quot;http://zurb.com/playground/twentytwenty&quot;&gt;TwentyTwenty&lt;/a&gt; for the image comparison, &lt;a href=&quot;http://leafletjs.com/&quot;&gt;Leaflet.js&lt;/a&gt; for the map, and &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.idangero.us/sliders/swiper/index.php&quot;&gt;Swiper&lt;/a&gt; for the photo gallery.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
